quran[52]{c,v,t}:
  69,1,"Eliatoto (lilirurila)."
  69,2,"Ne eliatoto (lilirurila) elo ni shina?"
  69,3,"Ne nishina shikhumanyia eliatoto elo?"
  69,4,"Abandu ba Tsamudi nende A’ad bakatsula amasila karenjinjia omwoyo."
  69,5,"Mana Abandu ba Tsamudi basishibwa nende amasila amakali."
  69,6,"Ne Abandu ba A’ad basishibwa nomuyeka kweyimbumbuyeka."
  69,7,"Okwayabarumila khubilo saba nende tsinyanga munane tsilondokhana, olola Abandu nibalambalile shinga emisala chia mitende emikhaya."
  69,8,"Kho ololangakhwo yesiyesi mubo watong’a?"
  69,9,"Ne Firauni niyetsa nende abali imbeli wuwe, nende tsingongo tsiakalukhanibwa hasi niba hekulu, okhurulana nende tsimbi tsiabu."
  69,10,"Nibakhaya okhuloonda Omurumwa wa Nyasaye wabu Omulesi, ne mana nabakhamara obutinyu muno."
  69,11,"Toto olwa amaatsi ketsula, khwabachinga Muliaro."
  69,12,"Khulwokhukhola ako kabe eshitsulisio khwinywe, ne shikawulile eshirwi shiokhuwulila."
  69,13,"Olwa olwika lulifurwamwo okhufurwa khulala."
  69,14,"Ne eshialo nende efikulu olwa bilichingwa, mana biswakwe okhuswakwa khulala."
  69,15,"Inyanga eyo niyo olwe indukho ilirulila."
  69,16,"Ne likulu lilirandukha, nalio inyanga eyo liliba liteshele."
  69,17,"Ne Abamalaika baliba khundulo khwalio, ne munane mubo balichinga eshifumbi shiobwami shia Omulesi wuwo hekulu wabu."
  69,18,"Inyanga eyo mulirebwa habulafu mwesi, ne shibulaho shiosishiosi shiliifisa mwinywe."
  69,19,"Kho ulia ulihebwa eshitabu shishie nomukhono omuluunji, aliboola mbu: “Itse musomekhwo eshitabu shianjie."
  69,20,"Toto bwene ndali ndamanya ndilinyola okhurebwa ebikhole bianje.”"
  69,21,"Kho aliba mubulamu buchamisia."
  69,22,"Mumukunda kwomwikulu kwa hekulu."
  69,23,"Ebiamo biakwo bili ahambi."
  69,24,"“Lie mana munywe mubusangafu okhurulana nende kamwaranjilisia mutsinyanga tsiabura (khushialo).”"
  69,25,"Ne ulia ulihebwa eshitabo shishie nomukhono omukhasi, aliboola mbu: “Manyanga ekhaya okhuhebwa eshitabu shianje."
  69,26,"Mana kata ekhayanga okhumanya shinga ndilirebwa ebikhole bianje."
  69,27,"Aaah bayee liakhaberesa lifwa elala (ndakhaya okhulamusibwa)."
  69,28,"Emiandu chianje shichiakhoonya shiosishiosi tawe."
  69,29,"Obwami bwanje buuwerekhwo!”"
  69,30,"Mumubukule mana mumuboye."
  69,31,"Mana mumusukune mumulilo."
  69,32,"Mana mumuboyokanie nomunyororo kweshichelo shiemikhono amakhumi saba."
  69,33,"Toto bwene shiyali yasuubila Nyasaye woluyali tawe."
  69,34,"Ne shiyatinyisinjia okhulisia abamanani tawe."
  69,35,"Mana lwalelo ano abula Omulina."
  69,36,"Nohomba eshiakhulia halali ghislin (amafila)."
  69,37,"Shibashiliitsanga tawe halali Abandu betsimbi."
  69,38,"Ne nditsuba khubia mulolanga."
  69,39,"Nende khubia mulalolanga tawe."
  69,40,"Toto bwene namakhuwa ka Omurumwa Owoluyali."
  69,41,"Ne shinamakhuwa ka omwimbi wa mashairi tawe. Obusubili bwenyu nibutiti po."
  69,42,"Nohomba shinamakhuwa komufumu tawe. Okhwitsulila khwenyu nokhutiti muno."
  69,43,"Keshibwa okhurula khu Nyasaye Omulesi webiloonje bioosi."
  69,44,"Ne akhuchishilanga amakhuwa kandi."
  69,45,"Toto khwakhamutilile nende omukhono omulunji."
  69,46,"Mana khwakhamukhalache omusi omukhongo kwomwoyo."
  69,47,"Ne awumao yesiyesi mwinywe wakhakhwikaliile."
  69,48,"Ne ako ni amachelo khubaria Nyasaye."
  69,49,"Ne toto bwene khwamanya mbu mwinywe balimwo abakhayi."
  69,50,"Ne toto bwene abakhayi baliyitsulisia."
  69,51,"Ne toto nobwatoto bubulamwo tsinganakani."
  69,52,"Kho mana tswenula elira lia Nyasaye wuwo Woluyali."
